We're so excited to finally be sharing this!! We have been working hard over the past 6 months to bring you @sparkbyseekdiscomfort Spark is a game that prompts you with questions to connect with those around you, and then sends you on a random adventure to be able to deepen those connections! It is our ultimate goal with Yes Theory to give you tools to Seek Discomfort in your own life, and that's exactly what Spark is.

We asked you all what were the best questions you've had in your life to connect with other people, and that's where the inspiration for all of these questions came from! And one of the best parts is that the adventures that the Spark generates are ever evolving, so the game will never be the same! (Secret tip, the flow and adventure element of the game was designed by our very own in house architect @ammar üòÉ) 

Spark by Seek Discomfort is launching this Sunday, 2/27 @ 10 am PST!!
